OL,3,CMan set fire to his ex-wife house in
OL,4,C'terrifying plot to kill her'
OL,6,FA man who set fire to his ex-wife
OL,7,Fhouse in a "terrifying plot to kill
OL,8,Fher" has been convicted of attempted
OL,9,Fmurder.
OL,11,FNicholas Martin, 63, from Eccles in
OL,12,FSalford, struck in the middle of the
OL,13,Fnight as his ex-partner slept, pouring
OL,14,Fpetrol through her letterbox.
OL,16,FEmma Martin was forced to escape the
OL,17,Fblaze by jumping from her first floor
OL,18,Fwindow, leaving her with serious
OL,19,Finjuries. The court heard she was
OL,20,F"lucky to survive the attack."
