OL,6,F"I hope the outcome allows her to
OL,7,Fbegin moving forward with her life,
OL,8,Fknowing he will face the consequences
OL,9,Fof his horrifying actions."
OL,11,FNicholas Martin met his former wife in
OL,12,F2019 on a dating app, and subjected
OL,13,Fher to a "prolonged attack" just two
OL,14,Fyears later.
OL,16,FIn August 2021 the couple went to
OL,17,FScotland where Martin subjected his
OL,18,Fwife to a vicious attack in their
OL,19,Fholiday accommodation.
