OL,6,FHe hit her against the walls and floor
OL,7,Fand would not allow her to leave the
OL,8,Froom, leaving her with extensive
OL,9,Fbruising.
OL,11,FOn 14 September 2024, Martin was
OL,12,Fcharged with assault occasioning
OL,13,Factual bodily harm and released on
OL,14,Fbail conditions to live in Leicester,
OL,15,Fand to have no contact with his ex-
OL,16,Fpartner.
