OL,3,CMan set fire to his ex-wife house in
OL,4,C'terrifying plot to kill her'
OL,6,FBut Martin broke his bail conditions
OL,7,Fafter travelling to Worsley on 21
OL,8,FOctober 2024, where he booked into a
OL,9,Fhotel and waited until the middle of
OL,10,Fthe night to execute his plans while
OL,11,Fhis ex-wife slept.
OL,13,FAt 4.15am the following morning, he
OL,14,Fdrove to her house, setting alight
OL,15,Fpetrol he had poured through the
OL,16,Fletterbox before fleeing.
OL,18,FLater that morning, in an attempt to
OL,19,Fevade arrest, he booked into a hotel
OL,20,Fin Windermere in the Lake District.
