OL,3,CMan set fire to his ex-wife house in
OL,4,C'terrifying plot to kill her'
OL,6,FHer only escape was to jump from a
OL,7,Ffirst-floor window, breaking both her
OL,8,Fankles and a vertebrae in her back.
OL,10,FMartin was arrested on 23 October
OL,11,F2024, at a hotel in the Lake District,
OL,12,Fwhere a petrol can containing petrol
OL,13,Fwas recovered.
OL,15,FHe pleaded not guilty at court, later
OL,16,Fadmitting to causing the fire, but
OL,17,Fdenied plans to kill.
OL,19,FGiving evidence, Martin told jurors: "
OL,20,FI wanted to try and see (her) and the
OL,21,Fcat."
